  <brief_title>Perioperative Management and Outcomes of Minimally Invasive Esophagectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Perioperative Management and Outcomes of Minimally Invasive Esophagectomy- Experience of a High-volume Tertiary Center in Taiwan</official_title>
